OpenAI response for Prompt:  write a 100 word essay on a water bottle 
 ********************************** 



A water bottle is an important everyday item. It is used for storing and carrying water, and is often used as a means of staying hydrated throughout the day. Its design is simple, but it is an effective and convenient way to keep water close at hand. Water bottles come in a variety of shapes, sizes, and materials, making them customizable to individual needs. They can also be insulated to keep water cold or hot. Many water bottles even have filters to ensure the water is clean and safe to drink. Water bottles are essential for those on-the-go, providing an easy and convenient way to stay hydrated.